            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間16日11:03，恆生科技指數下跌199.04點（或4%），暫報4782.56點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+9.05%</li><li>近 1 月：-15.29%</li><li>近 3 月：+14.16%</li><li>近 6 月：+11.92%</li><li>今年以來：+11.49%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>衛星及無?通訊概念領跌-7.36%。其中    中播數據(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00471:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00471\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00471-HK</a>)            下跌        20.9%            ;        亞太衛星(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01045:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01045\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01045-HK</a>)            下跌        2.11%            ;        中國鐵塔(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00788:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00788\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00788-HK</a>)            上漲        0.92%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大中華區概念領跌-4.13%。其中    ＸＬ二南方恒科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07226:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07226\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07226-HK</a>)            下跌        6.66%            ;        ＦＬ二南方國指(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07288:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"ht